              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer576825586999658836"> I liked this book. Its a good fast read and a pretty good first novel. I liked Konowa as a character a lot, however where I thought the book was deficient was in explaining the iron elves, how they got guns etc.<br/><br/>We never learn who all of the characters are and we do not learn all of the powers of the magical people, but clearly the book is part of a trilogy so I would expect to get more information later.<br/><br/></span>

