        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer317746191" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer15656195888098499944">Not impressed with the story. Main characters weren’t interesting. Couple of secondary characters were better. </span>

          </span>
